1.audition_text: Commander, I've reserved the tearoom for today. Why don't we use this opportunity to take a load off?
1.name: Tearoom Leisure
1.overview: You're alone with Chen Hai in the serene tea room. She gives you a lap pillow to ease your fatigue, and something special on top of that...

2.audition_text: Whew... That was fun! Heehee. I got a bit carried away. It's been quite a while since we played on the beach like this...
2.name: On the Beach With Kashino
2.overview:
"Do you like the beach, Commander? I really love it here."
Enjoy the sunshine and shimmering waves with Kashino.
Even the refreshing breeze and waves cannot cool her passion.

3.audition_text: (Commander's scent... I wonder if it's okay for me to get a little closer...)
3.name: In the Infirmary With Janus
3.overview:
A girl's warmth right by your pillow
Her earnest desire to be by your side
comes to you as whispers by your bedside

4.audition_text: You can't ride a Ferris wheel and NOT kiss at the top♪ It'll be a memory you can cherish forever, honey♡
4.name: Sweetness that Melts in the Mouth
4.overview: Ice cream on a Ferris wheel is sweet, but this moment with New Jersey is many times sweeter.

5.audition_text: Relax, now. There is nothing you have to be embarrassed of.
5.name: The Greatest Reward
5.overview: It's a dull afternoon. Emden has come, offering you a reward almost too good for a mere human.

6.audition_text: Anyway, that dummy sure is taking long... How long am I gonna have to wait here?
6.name: A Gift From... Hammann?
6.overview: Hammann tries to play a prank on you, only for it to backfire in your favor.

7.audition_text: In return... you could take a bite out of me. Whatever part you like.
7.name: Your Desire is All Mine
7.overview:
A tipsy moment with St. Louis. 
From her luscious lips, temptation flows forth...

8.audition_text: Just a little while longer. I want to stay immersed... in the harmony of our beating hearts...
8.name: Symphonious Heartbeats
8.overview: An earbud cord brings you and Helena closer and closer. Is that static noise you hear? No, it's a steady throb; the most precious thing...

9.audition_text: My, I can't tell what you're thinking at all, Commander. Shall we take a short break first? After all... the real deal is still ahead of us.
9.name: Slightly Feverish Kitchen
9.overview: Ting An, while showing off her cooking skills, also wants to offer some tips for making dim sum. In this hot and humid kitchen, the temperature between the two of you is also rising...

10.audition_text: Heehee... That's right. I might get sooo exhausted that I won't be able to move a muscle~
10.name: A Girl's Secret Plans
10.overview: San Jacinto invites you to give her swimming lessons. The girl's laughter, the splashing water... The two of you soon end up with time all to yourselves. Will her heart-throbbing plan come to fruition?

11.audition_text: Hm? You say you're... intoxicated by my voice? It's "as sweet as nectar"?
11.name: Intoxicated by Lingering Sounds
11.overview: You happen to run into Unzen while she is reading in the library.As the two of you read together, the atmosphere gradually becomes hazy to the sound of Unzen's voice–
